    Class Description
    DctCalculator
    DctCalculator This class can be used to track the changing matrix sparsity for an image that is being modified.
    Image_Reconstructor
    Image_Reconstructor This class can be used to reconstruct the output images of Photon_Image_Processor, if there was not enough input data available.
    Image_Thresholder
    Image_Thresholder This class can be used to filter noise from the output image of Photon_Image_Processor.
    LogLikelihoodCalculator
    LogLikelihoodCalculator This class can be used to track the log likelihood for an image that is being modified.
    Photon_Image_Processor
    Photon_Image_Processor This class is able to process a stack containing single photon events data and create a combined hi-res image.
    Recursive_TIFF_Opener
    Recursive_TIFF_Opener This class can be used to open all TIFF files in a directory as virtual stack.
    SilentMaximumFinder
    This ImageJ plug-in filter finds the maxima (or minima) of an image.
    SilentRankFilters
    This plugin implements the Mean, Minimum, Maximum, Variance, Median, Open Maxima, Close Maxima, Remove Outliers, Remove NaNs and Despeckle commands.
